column2: SELECT p.ra,p.dec, p.z ,p.zErr, s.velDisp, s.velDispErr FROM SpecObj AS s JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS p ON s.specObjID = p.specObjID WHERE (p.ra between # and #) AND (p.dec between # and #) AND (p.petroMag_r - p.extinction_r<#) AND (p.zWarning=#) AND p.class= &&& AND p.subclass= &&& AND p.survey=&&& AND p.programname=&&&
